    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/e133c8b967f7971ffe34f854b5d91c8d.poster.avif?t=1755630764\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/e133c8b967f7971ffe34f854b5d91c8d.webm?t=1755630764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/e133c8b967f7971ffe34f854b5d91c8d.mp4?t=1755630764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a hypnotist whose name is all over 1930s Germany. You can do anything:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >read minds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >cast characters into a trance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >impersonate others</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >know the precise time of death of everyone including yourself</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/6bb7312e5c323d8af0ba83695754fb40.poster.avif?t=1755630764\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/6bb7312e5c323d8af0ba83695754fb40.webm?t=1755630764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/6bb7312e5c323d8af0ba83695754fb40.mp4?t=1755630764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/43ab678690bd589e6266e5e9fd98f4c0.poster.avif?t=1755630764\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/43ab678690bd589e6266e5e9fd98f4c0.webm?t=1755630764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/43ab678690bd589e6266e5e9fd98f4c0.mp4?t=1755630764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sounds hella nice, doesn’t it? Now imagine - one of your experiments goes awry and you swap fates. Which means:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you’re stuck with some alcoholic’s memories permanently in your mind</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >nightmares haunt you </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you’re a crime accomplice </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >but most importantly: you only have five hours to live</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/6ab5702b9b60d16ebc8c8bbc007dec52.poster.avif?t=1755630764\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/6ab5702b9b60d16ebc8c8bbc007dec52.webm?t=1755630764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/6ab5702b9b60d16ebc8c8bbc007dec52.mp4?t=1755630764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you unravel the mysteries of the past without going insane and turn back time? <br>The countdown’s on!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hypnosis as a core mechanic: explore and reshape other people's memories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Interactive dialogues with consequences and nonlinear progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Psychological puzzles based on logic and emotional insight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Read characters' thoughts to uncover inner conflicts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Atmosphere of paranoia, guilt, and fear — no jump scares</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Free exploration: choose your own order of scenes and conversations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Historical setting: Germany on the brink of dictatorship</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140780/extras/c3925265997c1b9a53e8db21c2f83236.avif?t=1755630764\" width=500 height=277 /></span></p>",
